  "body": "**Steps:**\r\n\r\n1. on mobile, create a community \r\n2. from mobile, invite desktop to this community\r\n3. on mobile (as admin) add a channel\r\n4. on desktop open this channel to keep it visible\r\n5. on mobile as admin , ban desktop user\r\n6. on desktop, as already banned user, send any message to channel in community\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1440\" alt=\"Screenshot 2021-05-06 at 15 07 42\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/82375995/117296082-4fecdc00-ae7d-11eb-8d96-afcd8ca04259.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n`DBG 2021-05-06 15:06:56+03:00 callPrivateRPC                             topics=\"rpc\" tid=505158 file=core.nim:20 rpc_method=wakuext_sendChatMessage\r\nERR 2021-05-06 15:06:56+03:00 rpc response error                         topics=\"rpc\" tid=505158 file=core.nim:24 result=\"{\\\"jsonrpc\\\":\\\"2.0\\\",\\\"id\\\":0,\\\"error\\\":{\\\"code\\\":-32000,\\\"message\\\":\\\"can\\'t post on chat\\\"}}\"\r\n`",
